window.bookSummaryJSON = "They were orphans, Chris and Saul - raised in a Philadelphia school for boys, bonded by friendship, and devoted to a mysterious man called Eliot. <p>He visited them and brought them candy.</p> <p>He treated them like sons.</p> <p>He trained them to be assassins.</p> <p>Now he is trying desperately to have them killed.</p> <p>Spanning the globe, here is an astonishing novel of fierce loyalty and violent betrayal, of murders planned and coolly executed, of revenge bitterly, urgently desired.</p>"; 
